h1. shiro:notUser

h2. Purpose
This tag only writes its body to the output if the current user
is neither logged in nor remembered from a previous session (via
the "remember me" cookie).


h2. Examples
{code}
<shiro:notUser>
 <span>
       Welcome, please sign in.
 </span>
 ...
</shiro:notUser>


{code}



